title: Start
body:
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Wonbo, this has been my dream:
To catch the fish, fillet it, and eat it.
FARM. TO. TABLE.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
(Rolling eyes)
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
No, I'm serious!
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
This isn't even fair to the fish. 
We have a giant block of bait below us.
This isn't really fishing.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
No, this is INTELLIGENT fishing.
